    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl> <ptr target="#oliverioTacc"/> <citedRange>II.53</citedRange></bibl>, whence
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SECir"/>, <citedRange>140</citedRange> (photo)</bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>098900</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#_μος"><gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/><seg part="F">μος</seg></name> 
                        <persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-63328"><name type="patronymic" nymRef="#Αὐτόβωλος">Αὐτοβώλω</name></persName></persName>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="divine" ref="#Apollo"><name nymRef="#Ἀπόλλων"><supplied reason="lost">Ἀπόλλ</supplied>ωνι</name></persName> <w lemma="δεκάτα">δεκάταν</w>
                    <lb n="2a"/><space quantity="3" unit="line"/>
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p>
                    <app loc="1">
                        <lem><gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/>μος</lem>
                        <rdg resp="#SECir"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>μος</rdg>
                    </app>
                </p>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>mos fils d'Autobolos <supplied reason="subaudible">a consacré ce monument</supplied> à Apollon au titre de la dîme.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>mos son of Autobolos <supplied reason="subaudible">dedicated this monument</supplied> to Apollo as a tithe.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>mos figlio di Autobolos <supplied reason="subaudible">ha dedicato questo monumento</supplied> ad Apollo come decima.</p>
            </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>Pugliese Carratelli at <bibl><ptr target="#SECir"/></bibl>, published this inscription from a photograph in the archive of the Department of Antiquities and a drawing found in Oliverio's papers.
                 From them he was also able to mention the findspot.</p>
	<p/>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
